    <summary>Easily and automatically resize your source image assets as part of your build process.</summary>
    <description>
      Easily and automatically resize your source image assets as part of your build process.

      iOS:
       - @1x, @2x, @3x

      Android:
       - All the dpi's (eg: ldpi, mdpi, hdpi, xhdpi, etc.)
       - Any custom dpi folder (eg: drawable-large-land-mdpi)

      UWP:
       - No explicit support yet, but very possible to still use custom outputs with already!
    </description>
